   <body>
      <prereq>
         <ul>
            <li>  The status of the record is either <uicontrol>Awaiting</uicontrol> or <uicontrol>Delegated</uicontrol>.</li>
         </ul>
      </prereq>
      <context>You can view delegation details. </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>In the module menu, click<uicontrol>Administration</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The<uicontrol>ADMINISTRATION</uicontrol>page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the navigation pane, expand<uicontrol>User Management</uicontrol>, and then click <uicontrol>Delegation of Authority</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The<uicontrol>DELEGATION OF AUTHORITY</uicontrol>list page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select the appropriate record, and then click<uicontrol>View</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The<uicontrol>DELEGATION OF AUTHORITY</uicontrol>page is displayed.</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>Is Delegated</uicontrol>check box is selected by default for the delegated projects or contracts.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click<uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
